## Existing Technical Plan (Original Draft)

### Tech Stack

#### Frontend
- Next.js (React)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS or custom CSS
- Vercel hosting

#### Backend
- Next.js API routes
- Node.js
- Authentication (NextAuth or custom)

#### Database
- PostgreSQL or MongoDB
- Hosted on Supabase, PlanetScale, or MongoDB Atlas

#### Real-Time Messaging
- WebSockets or Pusher

#### Payments
- Stripe

